OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry and
OL,6,Fclear to start the evening for most,
OL,7,Fand feeling chilly. Cloud building as
OL,8,Fthe night progresses, perhaps bringing
OL,9,Fthe odd spot of drizzle. Temperatures
OL,10,Frising somewhat as skies turn overcast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FCloud and any drizzle
OL,13,Fclearing during the morning. Then a
OL,14,Fdry day with a good number of pleasant
OL,15,Fsunny spells and feeling mild. A
OL,16,Flittle breezy by the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
