OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FMild
OL,6,Fand bright again on Thursday, but rain
OL,7,Farriving later. Largely settled on
OL,8,FFriday and Saturday with further sunny
OL,9,Fspells, but temperatures returning to
OL,10,Fnearer average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
